name: gridspec
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "gridspec" %}
{% set version = "0.1.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/LiamBindle/gridspec/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 70c26b827f37116660d6eb564716cfe4fdb9501263529d4b156c2bcf9b100600

build:
  entry_points:
    - gridspec-create = gridspec.cli:create
    - gridspec-utils = gridspec.cli:utils
    - gridspec-dump = gridspec.cli:dump
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 0

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - click
    - netcdf4
    - numpy
    - pygeohash
    - python >=3.6
    - xarray

test:
  imports:
    - gridspec
  commands:
    - pip check
    - gridspec-create --help
    - gridspec-utils --help
    - gridspec-dump --help
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/LiamBindle/gridspec
  license: MIT
  license_file:
    - LICENSE
  summary: Utilities for working with gridspec files.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - LiamBindle
